## Migration Status

The codebase is currently undergoing a reorganization of utility modules to improve maintainability and organization. Adapter files are temporarily in place to ensure backward compatibility during this transition.

All adapters follow a similar pattern:

1. They are marked with comments indicating they are adapter files
2. They contain export statements that re-export from the new canonical location
3. They will emit deprecation warnings when imported directly

## Guidelines

- Do not modify adapter files directly
- Update imports to use the new canonical locations where possible
- Adapters will be removed once all imports throughout the codebase have been updated
